        <text><![CDATA[ <p><strong>Make Schools Safe Again Act</strong></p> <p>This bill prohibits the Department of Education and the Department of Justice from authorizing&nbsp;or encouraging a school to have a policy of not&nbsp;referring a student suspected of criminal activity to law enforcement.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
    </summaries>
    <title>Make Schools Safe Again Act</title>
    <titles>
      <item>
        <titleType>Display Title</titleType>
        <title>Make Schools Safe Again Act</title>
      </item>
      <item>
        <titleType>Official Title as Introduced</titleType>
        <title>To prohibit the Secretary of Education and the Attorney General from encouraging certain policies or agreements between elementary and secondary schools and local law enforcement agencies.</title>
        <billTextVersionName>Introduced in House</billTextVersionName>
        <billTextVersionCode>IH</billTextVersionCode>
